        <h1>FAQ</h1>
        
        <section>
          <Legend>For Posts:</Legend>
           <h2>How do I create a post?</h2>
             <p>1.Click the corresponding bottom on the dashboard; </p>
             <p>2.Fill all the required fields in the post page;</p>
             <p>(including the title/abstract/content/tags)</p>
             <p>3.Click the 'Submit' bottom to submit your post.</p>
             <p>(you can click the 'clear' bottom if you fill something wrong)</p>
             <hr/>
           <h2>How do I delete/edit a post?</h2>
             <p>1.Check the list of post you have created;</p>
             <p>2.Click the post for which you want to delete/edit;</p>
             <p>3.Fill and submit the form just like what you did when created it.</p>
             <hr/>
            <h2>How do I approve a post?</h2>
             <p>1.Check the list of post;</p>
             <p>2.Click the box to approve the post.</p>
        </section>
        <section>
            <Legend>Other functions</legend>
            <h2>How do I update my account details?</h2>
            <p>1.Click the corresponding link ('Edit the details') on the left of the dashboard;</p>
            <p>2.Choose an option;</p>
            <p>3.Edit the details;</p>
            <p>3.Click the 'Submit' bottom to submit your update.</p>
            <p>(you can click the 'clear' bottom if you fill something wrong)</p>
            <hr/>
            <h2>How do I get to my charity site</h2>
            <p>Click the corresponding link ('My charity') on the left of the dashboard;</p>
            <hr/>
        </section>
